channel.title: Begin Of My ServerConsole (GUI)
channel.description:
Im on the project RuneBlaze This production is RuneBlaze(c)
Members: SamuraiBlood2 Zenzie Dune Blake(Guardian) for some strange reason :| Ringer24 Guthan38
/*END OF INTRO*/
I made this serverconsole .. Im not going to release this. I worked like 5Hours on it for the list itself Oh well here are the screens
ServerConsole: Here you will see if some player join, got banned, got muted, kicked, left server Im adding in a restarter to ;) **HINT: check menubar** You will also be able to typ commands in it probally to load scripts like AutoSpawn, NPC,.... Everything will be recorded into a file [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img113.imageshack.us/img113/9084/jkhjjzt6.png[/img][/URL]
SeverConsole PlayerHandler: Here you will see all player names with some buttons Details will open a screen with all stats, items he's carrying on his body, inventory I will also add a button BANK (well support me im going to add strings, so you see item name instead of item number) This will be supported in the ServerConsole and when you press the button ((going to add in menubar)) A tiptoolbox will pop open with it! [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img507.imageshack.us/img507/1408/jhjhghjjbs6.png[/img][/URL]
There isnt nothing much to see but whenI hoked it up to my server you'll see it. Post if you like :), Else hate it :(
